title: '"People organize to maintain a range of homeostasis in any number of areas, from proximity to other people to levels of conflict with other people"'
pid: b25d8002-d45b-414e-8a60-b2986b82df39
body: |2-
  "In addition, each person contains a multitude of cybernetic subsystems, from those that regulate blood sugar levels to those that regulate the expression of feelings."
